TenantSecurityLicense.name: TenantSecurityLicense
TenantSecurityLicense.description: Stores license usage information within Security Center.

Action.description: The type of change made to the license. Possible values are: ADDED REMOVED UPDATED

ActionDate.description: The timestamp for when this change was made.

DetailIdentifier.description: The unique identifier for this detail record.

ExpirationDate.description: The date on which this license expires.

MetricIdentifier.description: The ID of the corresponding TenantSecurityMonitorMetric.

MetricsType.description: The type of license collected by this metric.

Tenant.description: The ID of the tenant with this license.

TenantName.description: The name of the tenant with this license.

UsedLicensesLastUpdated.description: The date that the used licenses were last updated for this tenant.
